⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Spinners
node LMZ · LMZ · ⟦The Spinners:LMZ:6afbe8⟧

WHO   — The Spinners — levitating force-field stones
WHAT  — Wonder you can hold: the most toy-like of the gifts, and the one that marks Emma as the more gifted child.
WHERE — LMZ · The Last Mimzy (2007)  Framework inputs: The Last Mimzy (2007, dir. Robert Shaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film makes its magic tactile — stones that float at a child's will.
HOW   — By rising and forming a shimmering field when Emma turns her attention to them.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  We are stones that should sit still. In her hands we rise and spin and throw a wall of light — because she, alone, can ask us to.

